  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Working for Cabinet Office
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Operating at the heart of government, Cabinet Office is a vibrant and diverse place to work. 
  </p>

      
