<h2 id="cabinet-office-alumni-network">Cabinet Office alumni network</h2>

<p>Over time, Cabinet Office has benefited from an exceptionally talented and diverse group of employees.</p>

<p>The Cabinet Office alumni network maintains connections between current employees and alumni, and improves access to organisational knowledge and experience. It provides information on events, opportunities for innovation and open policy making by accessing alumni’s professional experience.</p>

<p>Sign up to the <a rel="external" href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/cabinet-office">LinkedIn Cabinet Office group</a> to join the network, connect with hundreds of colleagues past and present, and find out about the latest events and notifications.</p>

<p>If you prefer not to join LinkedIn, sign up to the <a href="mailto:alumni@cabinetoffice.gov.uk">Cabinet Office alumni mailing list</a> for news and notifications of events. If your details change, please update these via the link at the end of any event or welcome emails. For any general queries, please email <a href="mailto:alumni@cabinetoffice.gov.uk">alumni@cabinetoffice.gov.uk</a>.</p>

